sentences.sentence: The wind blown from the fens was damp.

sentences.sentence: Groom presented her work today at the Forum of European Neuroscience (Fens) conference in Amsterdam.

sentences.sentence: Michael Douglas plays the part of “D-Fens, ” a normal man who has a terrible day during an unusually hot Los Angeles summer day.
sentences.translation: 迈克尔 道格拉斯扮演“D-Fens”的角色，这是一个普通的人，他度过了洛杉矶超级炎热夏日中糟糕的一天。
